SchemeName.Name: LV:Supervision/Accreditation Status List of certification services from Certification Service Providers, which are supervised/accredited by the referenced Scheme Operator’s Member State for compliance with the relevant provisions laid down in Directive 1999/93/EC of the European Parliament and of the Council of 13 December 1999 on a Community framework for electronic signatures.

PolicyOrLegalNotice.TSLLegalNotice: The applicable legal framework for the present TSL implementation of the Trusted List of supervised/accredited Certification Service Providers for Latvia is Directive 1999/93/EC of the European Parliament and of the Council of 13 December 1999 on a Community framework for electronic signatures and its implementation in Latvia laws.

Uzticamajā sarakstā iekļauto Latvijas kontrolēto/akreditēto sertifikācijas pakalpojumu sniedzēju pašreizējo uzticamo sarakstu (TSL) ieviešanas tiesisko pamatu nosaka Eiropas Parlamenta un Padomes 1999. gada 13. decembra Direktīva nr. 1999/93/EC par Kopienas pamatnostādnēm elektroniskā paraksta jomā, kā arī Latvijas normatīvi, kas attiecas uz elektroniskā paraksta ieviešanu Latvijā.
